OL,6,FBME workers were said to be
OL,7,F"significantly overrepresented" on
OL,8,Fzero-hours contracts compared with
OL,9,Fwhite workers.
OL,11,FThe TUC said its report, published
OL,12,Fahead of its Black Workers Conference
OL,13,Fon Saturday, showed that the
OL,14,Fdisproportionate number of BME workers
OL,15,Fon zero-hours contracts is a "prime
OL,16,Fexample" of structural racism in
OL,17,Faction.
